{"tid":1180751,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我可以點做？","createTime":"2019-06-01T05:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T16:51:36.000Z","uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2bdfcf77242c9f2fda1f779d7a84a5071f547d19","tid":1180751,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n平時我同老豆唔多會傾政治嘢<br />\n但係我哋關係幾好<br />\n就諗住send白宮條link叫佢簽<br />\n好奇之下我問佢支持定反對送中條例<br />\n佢話支持  我以為條問題有Bug<br />\n咁我再問多次佢係支持/中立/冇意見/反對<br />\n點知佢都係話支持<br />\n我問原因  佢答行得正企得正驚咩<br />\n我同佢講如果五毛狗或者臭蝗砌鳩咁點算<br />\n佢仲好撚淡定咁話點會呀 我都冇乜價値<br />\n我唔想有機會冇咗個老豆<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247b81953680d14279679d0458e317d5c45393a5","tid":1180751,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afc468451e9838ac4ff4e19e3725bbf184593df","tid":1180751,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded1bdfc8715f9f5f0e34dbf8636ce5902e3fdc8","tid":1180751,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3a198b7eee575626c235b2651ca35b9552d4f3","tid":1180751,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723e1b61215eeb15fd4e0ab536a14af722439c7f","tid":1180751,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以教下我點做<br />\n唔想再傾落去破壞關係<br />\n又想佢轉立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcfa36b6f9f102fd8749ab633d3b5723a68db06","tid":1180751,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB